Package com.layers.app.business

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ActivityBusinessInterface
    Contracts the respective business service for dependency injection.
    LiquorBusinessInterface
    Contracts the respective business service for dependency injection.
    LocationBusinessInterface
    Contracts the respective business service for dependency injection.
    ScaleBusinessInterface
    Contracts the respective business service for dependency injection.
    UserBusinessInterface
    Contracts the respective business service for dependency injection.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActivityBusinessService
    Activity business service handles the user activity logged from the controllers.
    LiquorBusinessService
    Liquor business service handles all the requests related to the inventory management feature of the application.
    LocationBusinessService
    Location business service handles the vendor permission requests to assemble relevant data to the locations the vendor wants to be either added, modified, removed, or viewed.
    ScaleBusinessService
    Scale business service handles scale related requests that involve assembling data, modifying liquor and scale configurations, and removing scales based on the location or business that is implementing the request.
    UserBusinessService
    User business service handles requests specific to the users account.
